data.description: Come home to beautiful country living with 3 acres to enjoy in Van Buren! The later summer sunsets can be seen from the covered back patio while grilling dinner for your guests or if preferred catching a sunrise might brightened your day from the porch that was built for sitting on and with a great cup of coffee! This stunning home features a large kitchen with granite counters, ample cabinet space, pantry living space, office/second living space, formal dining room, and four bedrooms along with 2.5 baths. The primary suite includes a huge bedroom, walk-in closet, beautiful, tiled shower and whirlpool tub for bubble baths after a long day!  Call for an appointment today!
